<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Walker_Percy&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8" title="Edit section: Further reading">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Further reading</span></h2>
<ul>
<li>Coles, Robert, <i>Walker Percy: An American Search</i>. Little, Brown &amp; Co, 1979.</li>
