<li>Samway, Patrick, <i>Walker Percy: A Life</i>. Loyola Press USA, 1999.</li>
<li>Tolson, Jay, <i>Pilgrim in the Ruins: A Life of Walker Percy</i>. New York: Simon and Schuster, 1992.</li>
<li>Wood, Ralph C, <i>The Comedy of Redemption: Christian Faith and Comic Vision in Four American Novelists</i>. University of Notre Dame Press, 1988.</li>
<li>Wyatt-Brown, Bertram. <i>House of Percy: Honor, Melancholy and Imagination in a Southern Family.</i> Oxford University Press USA, 1996.</li>
<li>_____. <i>The Literary Percys: Family History, Gender &amp; The Southern Imagination</i>. Athens and London: University of Georgia Press, 1994.</li>
</ul>
